{"tid":2449483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉業強：關注人大決定有關選委會組成未提及鄉議局","createTime":"2021-03-16T16:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T03:13:00.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a478758106c8fc52cf27872fedd716efe4d95b","tid":2449483,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:51:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580904-20210316.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580904-20210316.htm&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=375e40d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580904-20210316.htm&h=35f2ff7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580904-20210316.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n鄉議局主席劉業強表示，關注人大有關完善香港選舉制度的決定，未有在選委會的組成中提及鄉議局代表。他表示，堅決支持人大的決定，認為選委會將分成5個界別，當中地區和基層組織選委人數會增加，廣泛性增強，以達致均衡參與，相信在不同位置也可為市民發聲。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強說，傾向支持由選委會產生的立法會議席佔較重要的比例，建議佔35至40個議席，直選議席20至30個，功能組別議席30個，相信可令行政和立法上更暢順，估計中央認為香港過去20多年內耗嚴重，很多事情變得政治化，期望日後本港可集中推動經濟和民生。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強又指，未來立法會議席將增加，相信溫和的泛民主派議員也可入閘參選，不會「搞清一色」，立法會選舉不會成為「假選舉」。"},{"pid":"bfb03b73f8dc4368116d571530ec4aa512ad1cbf","tid":2449483,"uid":30274,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:53:28.000Z","msg":"廢物<br />\n你班鄉黑用完了, 可以丟棄<br />\n幫得共產黨就預左架啦"},{"pid":"a44c25d8ddccdf6af30b5062b383517a86e2ba7a","tid":2449483,"uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/01a4cab5a269c227d48bd236ea314823/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210213/_2021021309492365652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F01a4cab5a269c227d48bd236ea314823%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210213%2F_2021021309492365652.jpg&h=337d18f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img sr